="468" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="442" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ebe7356d03484071946a4c1c0b5cda89_r.jpg"/></figure><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br/></p><p>3. 关于镎-220抵达了核素图的一个叫作“质子滴线”的边界的具体情况，请看下图。</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br/></p><figure data-size="normal"><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f2dff35c40bc89761a81f0725471bee0_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="748" data-rawheight="467" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="748" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f2dff35c40bc89761a81f0725471bee0_r.jpg"/></figure><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br/></p><p>参考文献：</p><ol><li>Zhang Z Y, Gan Z G, Yang H B, et al. New Isotope Np 220: Probing the Robustness of the N= 126 Shell Closure in Neptunium[J]. Physical Review Letters, 2019, 122(19): 192503.</li><li>Zhang Z Y, Ma L, Gan Z G, et al. A gas-filled recoil separator, SHANS[J]. Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research Section B: Beam Interactions with Materials and Atoms, 2013, 317: 315-318.</li></ol>